Package model.entity

Class Room

java.lang.Object
model.entity.Room
public class Room
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a Room. A Room has several attributes to store the name, the position on the grid, and booleans to know if it is a starting point, if it is the room where the user can check the classification, if it can see the log, if it should register the log. It also has a list of connected rooms and if there is a vent room it has the name stored.
